The model addresses several issues in novel ways. It supports abstraction idioms commonly used by designers--for example, explicitly distinguishing different types of elements and providing type-specific analysis support. It specifies packaging properties as well as functional propertics of components-for example, distinguishing clearly between functionality delivered in the form of

